1. *Tragedija* se dogodila u petak uveče. (*Tragedy* happened on Friday evening.)
2. Bio je *tragičan* kraj večeri. (It was a *tragic* end to the evening.)
3. Glumac je odigrao ulogu u velikoj *tragediji*. (The actor played a role in a great *tragedy*.)
4. *Tragedija* se desila nakon što je avion pao. (*Tragedy* happened after the plane crashed.)
5. Iako su svi bili uzbuđeni zbog predstave, publika je bila zapanjena kada se *tragedija* dogodila. (Although everyone was excited about the performance, the audience was shocked when the *tragedy* happened.)
6. Njegov život je bio pun *tragedija* i prepreka. (His life was full of *tragedies* and obstacles.)
7. Povijest je puna *tragedija* koje se ponavljaju iznova i iznova. (History is full of *tragedies* that repeat themselves over and over again.)
8. *Tragedija* se dogodila u najgori mogući trenutak. (*Tragedy* happened at the worst possible moment.)
9. Ova knjiga je *tragična* priča o ljubavi i gubitku. (This book is a *tragic* story of love and loss.)
10. On je bio glavni junak u *tragediji* koja se dogodila. (He was the main character in the *tragedy* that happened.)